---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '~/components/Section.astro';
import { SITE } from '~/i18n/ui';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How NitroX Consulting handles the personal data you submit through this website."
  lang="en"
  path="/privacy"
>
  <Section title="Privacy Policy">
    <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-5 text-muted [&_h3]:mt-8 [&_h3]:text-lg [&_h3]:font-semibold [&_h3]:text-[var(--text)]">
      <p class="text-sm">Last updated: 2026-07-09</p>

      <h3>Who we are</h3>
      <p>
        This website is operated by {SITE.name}, a French company based in {SITE.location}. For any privacy question, contact us at
        <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`} class="underline">{SITE.email}</a>.
      </p>

      <h3>What we collect</h3>
      <p>
        We only collect the information you choose to send us through the contact form on this site — your name, email address and
        message. We do not sell data and we do not use it for marketing.
      </p>

      <h3>How your message is processed</h3>
      <p>
        Contact-form submissions are delivered over an encrypted connection to our own infrastructure and relayed to us by email via
        Amazon SES in the EU (Paris region). Your message is processed within the European Union. We use it solely to reply to you.
      </p>

      <h3>Retention</h3>
      <p>We keep contact messages only as long as needed to handle your enquiry and any resulting relationship, then delete them.</p>

      <h3>Your rights</h3>
      <p>
        Under the GDPR (RGPD) you may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data, and you may object to its
        processing. Email <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`} class="underline">{SITE.email}</a> and we will respond.
      </p>

      <h3>Cookies & analytics</h3>
      <p>This site does not set advertising cookies. Any analytics, if enabled, are privacy-respecting and EU-based.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>
